sect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.jdtounix-seealso">   <h3 class="title">参见</h3>   <span>    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link unixtojd()} - 转变Unix时间戳为Julian Day计数</span></li>     </ul>   </span>  </div>  <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.calendar.php">日历 函数</a></div></div>
